Use the standard library
This is how to fizz_buzz of n:
   Remember that fizz is 0
   Remember that buzz is 0
   Do this n times:
      Increase fizz
      Increase buzz
      When fizz is 3, then:
         Remember that fizz is 0
      End when
      When buzz is 5, then:
         Remember that buzz is 0
      End when
   End do
   When fizz is 0, then:
      When buzz is 0, then:
         The answer is 0
      But, if not:
         The answer is 1
      End when
   But, if not:
      When buzz is 0, then:
         The answer is 2
      But, if not:
         The answer is 3
      End when
   End when
